Lingua-JA-Summarize version 0.01
================================

Lingua::JA::Summarize is a keyword extractor / summary generator for
Japanese texts.  The module uses MeCab as a tokenizer.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

MeCab is required to use this module.

